😕 Don't know how to start keto diet properly? or want to lose 5-10 lbs in the first week alone with keto lifestyle ?
You can click link in our bio to get Everything You Need for keto Success. Imagine… armed with 4-week meal plan, 7 Keto guide books, and the 3 bonus guides… you’ll be able to start strong and finish strong. 💪 @ketomealrecipe 
.
You just can’t go wrong with pancakes, bacon and eggs👏⁣⁣
⁣
What are you making for breakfast?⁣⁣
⁣
I like both almond and coconut flour pancakes, which do you like best?⁣⁣
⁣
Save this post and share with friends that are starting keto 🙌⁣⁣
⁣

My fave is Maple and Chocolate!⁣⁣
⁣
I triple the recipe and store them in the freezer for easy breakfast options. Makes life so much easier!⁣⁣
⁣
For those of you that are new to my page, here is my blender pancake recipe 🤗⁣⁣
⁣
Throw everything in the blender, mix, cook and enjoy 🥳⁣⁣
⁣
Simple ingredients and kiddo approved🥰⁣⁣
⁣
Almond flour blender pancakes⁣⁣
⁣
4oz of cream cheese (microwave 15-30sec)⁣⁣
4 eggs (room temp)⁣⁣
3/4 cup of Almond flour⁣⁣
1 tsp baking powder⁣⁣
1-2 Tablespoons of sweetener ⁣⁣
1/2- 1tsp vanilla ⁣⁣
1/8 tsp Cinnamon⁣⁣
⁣
Coconut flour pancakes⁣⁣
⁣
•4oz cream cheese⁣⁣
•4eggs⁣⁣
•4 tableapoons of coconut flour⁣⁣
•1 1/2 teaspoons of baking powder⁣⁣
•1-2 tablespoons of sweetener⁣⁣
⁣
Optional but I always use⁣⁣
•1/2 tsp cinnamon⁣⁣
•1 tsp vanilla extract⁣⁣
•1/2 tsp maple extract⁣⁣
⁣
Directions:⁣⁣
-Put all ingredients in blender... blend for 45 seconds - 1 minute.⁣⁣
-Let sit for 10mins before cooking⁣⁣
-enjoy with butter and SF syrup *you can freeze and warm up in toaster or microwave⁣⁣
⁣
Who’s making pancakes?🙋‍♀️⁣⁣
_____________________⁣⁣

📋You need:
2 medium zucchini
4oz cream cheese
1/2 cup shredded mozzarella
1/4 cup shredded cheddar
1 jalapeño, diced
3 slices bacon, chopped
A pinch of salt
A dash of garlic powder .
.
Preheat oven to 450.
Slice zucchini in 1/4 slices but don’t cut all the way through! (Leave it like a fan)
Place zucchini on a tray and bake for 10 mins
Prep your cheese filling by combining all the cheeses, bacon, jalapeño and spices.
Fill in each section with the cheese mixture and bake another 8-9 mins. Enjoy!! 😍

❤Keto Cheddar Biscuits 🧀🥯😍 More easy and quick recipes are available in 28 day challenge @ketomealrecipe
⠀
Warning: These biscuits are delicious AF and it’s very easy to scarf down one too many. You’ve been warned.... 😉
Double taps if you love this
Credit: @keto_rebel

Anyone else starting to test out keto friendly recipes for Holidays? Make sure to save this one! These bad boys are super easy to whip up and you can’t even tell they’re keto. You can also make a bunch ahead of time to store in the fridge and reheat the next morning for breakfast sandwiches.
⠀
Here’s the recipe: ⤵️
Ingredients:
* 4 eggs
* 2 cups shredded sharp cheddar cheese
* 1 cup almond flour
* 2 tsp baking powder
* 2 tbsp butter melted
* 1 tsp garlic powder
* fresh parsley, for garnish
⠀
Instructions:
* Preheat the oven to 425F. Line a baking sheet with parchment paper.�
* Whisk the eggs in a bowl, then add cheddar cheese, melted butter, almond flour, baking powder, and garlic powder. Mix all the ingredients until well combined.�
* Use a large spoon to scoop the dough onto a baking sheet. Top with optional chopped parsley.�

If you practice intermittent fasting, it’s important to break your fast with a healthy meal. Have plenty of healthy fats and leafy vegetables. Today, I just wanted some breakfast 🥑 .
.
WHAT YOU WILL NEED:
1 box of natural pork breakfast sausages
1 teaspoon swerve brown sugar ( optional )
1 tablespoon of butter ( grass fed and unsalted )
Two eggs
1/2 avocado
Everything bagel seasoning
Salt, pepper, chilli flakes
.
I cooked sausages according to package intrusions. Once cooked thoroughly and brown, I removed them from the skillet, wiped it clean, added 1 tablespoon of butter and the brown sugar. I let it melt and then threw in the sausages, rolled them around and plated them. For the eggs I used the same skillet and cooked them in the sausage and butter mixture until over easy. Served with avocado and hot coffee ☕️. Yours truly 🍒
